{
  "id": "adv_card_mhk_10_01",
  "title": "miho",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん\nちょっとお願いしたいことがあるのですが、いいですか",
      "startTime": 2.4290328678,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "え、俺にですか！？\nmihoさんが俺に頼み事なんて、めずらしいですね",
      "startTime": 8.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "なぜそんなに驚かれたのか、想像は付きますが\n私だって不本意ですから、どうぞご安心下さい",
      "startTime": 16.6915157363,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "……まぁ、それはともかくとして\n今度、自分の車を買うつもりなんです",
      "startTime": 22.8333329518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "へぇ、それはいいですね\nあ、前に車のCMに出た時に、興味がわいたとか？",
      "startTime": 28.9937777128,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "それもありますが……今度の年末に\nスリクスの公式チャンネルを立ち上げるでしょう",
      "startTime": 37.4666662852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "kanaがネタを出せとうるさいので\n高額の買い物であれば、文句は言われないだろうと",
      "startTime": 43.0666662852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "それに車があれば、スタジオに移動するにしても\nfranとkanaと一緒に電車に乗らずに済みますし",
      "startTime": 50.4096971247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "……と、言う訳なので。今度の休日\n展示場に車を見に行くのに、付き合ってほしいんです",
      "startTime": 56.6333329518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "それは構わないんですけど……\nせっかくの買い物に付き合うのが、俺でいいんですか？",
      "startTime": 62.7318267982,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "さっき、チャンネルを立ち上げる話をしたでしょう\n私が車を買うところを、横で撮っていてほしいんです",
      "startTime": 70.3666662852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "あ……あぁ、そういうことだったんですね\nでもそれなら、kanaさんかfranさんの方が……",
      "startTime": 78.1666662852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "あの二人が、撮影係なんて引き受けると思います？\n聞くだけ無駄というものですね",
      "startTime": 85.4666632335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……ですよね、はい",
      "startTime": 87.7634202323,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_musicprogram-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "musicprogram-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.4200868131
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_musicprogram-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "musicprogram-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.4200868131
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "今日は、車のショールームにやって来ました\nここで、素敵な一台に出会えたらいいなと思っています",
      "startTime": 96.4666632335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_musicprogram-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "musicprogram-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.8900866987
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01-mhk011.m4a",
      "text": "それと、アドバイザーとして\nマネージャーさんにも、付いてきてもらいました",
      "startTime": 102.6666632335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01-mhk012.m4a",
      "text": "私は、車にはあまり詳しくないので……\n今日は、よろしくお願いしますね",
      "startTime": 108.8383983448,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_musicprogram-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "musicprogram-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.9068213305
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "は、はい。なんとか頑張らせていただきます",
      "startTime": 110.9068213305,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_musicprogram-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "musicprogram-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.11276234
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01-mhk013.m4a",
      "text": "ショールームの方に、撮影許可はいただいてますけど\n恥ずかしい真似は、しないで下さいよ",
      "startTime": 118.6333299001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（それに、俺の声も動画に入るんだよな）\n（だとしたら、あまり迂闊なことは言えないな……）",
      "startTime": 124.7552698627,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_musicprogram-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "musicprogram-00-noon",
      "startTime": 129.1301089129
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01-mhk014.m4a",
      "text": "こちらが今日お世話になる、ディーラーさんです\n初心者ですけれども、よろしくお願いしますね",
      "startTime": 133.3666632335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_musicprogram-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "musicprogram-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.709587749
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01-mhk015.m4a",
      "text": "以前、CMのお仕事をいただいた時に\nこちらの車に、すっかり惚れ込んでしまいまして",
      "startTime": 139.6999965668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_musicprogram-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "musicprogram-00-noon",
      "startTime": 147.0999965668
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01-mhk016.m4a",
      "text": "ですので今日はそちらをメインに見せていただければと\n……はい、よろしくお願いしますね",
      "startTime": 147.0999965668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "このメーカーの車に、もう決めてるみたいですけど\nいろいろ見て回らなくていいんですか？",
      "startTime": 153.0999955495,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_musicprogram-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "musicprogram-00-noon",
      "startTime": 155.7123399895
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01-mhk017.m4a",
      "text": "スポンサーの商品を使っていれば、印象もいいですし\nまたお仕事をもらえるかもしれないでしょう",
      "startTime": 159.4333390554,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "……さすがでございます",
      "startTime": 162.2190068087,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_musicprogram-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "musicprogram-00-noon",
      "startTime": 164.4923401516
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "いやーしかし、外国の車って格好いいというか\n色気みたいなものがありますよね",
      "startTime": 168.9333390554,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "俺も、いずれはこんないい車に乗ってみたいですよ\n………………ひえっ！？",
      "startTime": 176.2666642507,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_musicprogram-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "musicprogram-00-noon",
      "startTime": 177.4389904658
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01-mhk018.m4a",
      "text": "なんなんですか。いきなり変な声を出して",
      "startTime": 177.4389904658,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_musicprogram-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "musicprogram-00-noon",
      "startTime": 180.5906684716
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01-mhk019.m4a",
      "text": "あちらでディーラーさんも妙な顔をしていますよ\nまったく、恥ずかしい思いをさせないで下さい",
      "startTime": 183.699989446,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "す、すみません……その、ちょっとお値段が\n俺みたいな小市民には、あまり良くない額だったもんで",
      "startTime": 191.6333227794,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_musicprogram-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "musicprogram-00-noon",
      "startTime": 195.9442058723
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01-mhk020.m4a",
      "text": "貴方だって一応は、芸能関係者なんですから\n高級品も、眺める機会ならいくらでもあるでしょう",
      "startTime": 199.3442058723,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_musicprogram-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "musicprogram-00-noon",
      "startTime": 202.5891038419
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_01-mhk021.m4a",
